/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鶴咀犯法架原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鶴咀道未入迴旋處之前係合法<br />\n但果度有新巴9號鶴咀特別車經過<br />\n所以並不乎合「有車先去到」的原則<br />\n故推斷指為迴旋處後至低台發射站的一段<br />\n<br />\n該段除的士及授權車輛外，嚴禁進入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca229fb639de3df863b5c2acba48a005c751555","tid":61244,"uid":1868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飛鵝山頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山腰你都去唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太易去<br />\n平日都勁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8948efed71896adb8586e69e0015c0628e592ef","tid":61244,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"紅花嶺<br />\n上水華山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炒落山唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}